reviews.text: Table service was great, we worked our way through a lot of the menu as we came twice during our stay. The favourite was the KGB. I mean not only was it delicious, it comes in a tub with rubber ducky. What's not to like?
Different kinds of gin to try.  Interesting
Ran up quite the Bar tab between 2 of us. Good cocktails
Great little gin bar, plenty to choose from. Cozy atmosphere
Good cocktails for Hong Kong.
